assemblage.p:
The component of a vector {\bf{F}} in the direction of vector {\bf{v}} is
    \blert{\text{comp}_{\bf{v}}{\bf{F}} = \|{\bf{F}}\| \cos \theta} 
where \theta is the angle between {\bf{F}} and {\bf{v}}.

